<p><b> Put a Fork in Her.... Mother of All = done...</b></p>

<p>I had always KNOWN how gay PoG was, but that didn't stop the nagging voice in the back of my head: "Must kill slutty HO'" "Must kill SLUTTY HO!" <br />
<br />
It was getting louder and louder, every damned day. Well, today, the voice stopped. The Mother-of-All gracefully bowed down to the combined forces of FoH and CD. Loot? Well, it sucked.... For the ridiculously retarded effort we had to put in (clearing the zone) to kill her, and the fifteen+ minute fight of a flurrying 925quadding slut... IT REALLY SUCKED.<br />
<br />
Anyhow, here's the lewtz.<br />
<br />
Not ONE, but TWO, Plane of Growth Necromancer Robes! And a Sword, this sword:<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
P.S. For you newbies, Mother-of-All is Tunare, goddess of the gay, prancing, singing, sissy Elves...<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><br>
